title: Beautiful Renovated & Spacious 2 Bedroom Townhome
posting_body: ['Beautifully & newly renovated 2 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom 3-story townhome with its own private attached garage & driveway in a quiet and welcoming community that’s walking distance to all the places the neighborhood has to offer.', 'Featuring 1,650 square feet of living space with true condominium construction & soundproofing, the townhome also has a spacious den with a sliding door leading to its backyard that can be used as an office, playroom, or extra family room.', 'The open kitchen features stainless steel appliances and modern quartz countertops.', 'The main bedroom has its own walk-in closet & private bath.', 'Note: These photos are of a model home.', 'Color of cabinets and flooring may vary.', 'A comprehensive reusable tenant screening report made available to the landlord by a consumer reporting agency will not be accepted.', 'Available now at Martha Lake Townhomes!', 'Call', 'show contact info', 'for more information or to schedule a tour.', 'Townhome Features:', 'Engineered hardwood floors', 'Full size washer & dryer', 'Walk-in closet', 'Bonus den on 1st floor', '2 parking spaces: 1 inside garage, 1 in driveway', 'High-Speed Internet', 'Kitchen Details:', 'Stainless steel appliances', 'Quartz countertops', 'Breakfast bar', 'Dishwasher', 'Building Amenities:', 'Green and barbecue areas', 'Playground', 'Neighborhood Features:', 'Just a few short blocks from Walgreens, Walmart, QFC, Safeway, and Starbucks for all your everyday necessities.', 'Located next to the I-5 and I-405 corridor; ideal for your convenient commutes.', 'For your days off, we are just minutes away from Alderwood Mall, Martha Lake recreations and walking distance to restaurants.', 'Pricing Details:', 'Good credit required', 'Income must be at least 2.5 times the rental rate', 'Application fee: $50.00 per adult applicant', 'Security Deposits start at: $1,000.00', 'Non-refundable fee: $300.00', 'Utilities: Resident pays for electric, water, sewer, trash', 'Lease term: 12 months', 'Pet Policy: Pets welcome with some restrictions', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs allowed', '$250.00 refundable deposit', '$250.00 non-refundable fee', 'Pet rent: $25.00 cats, $35.00 dogs', 'Liability Insurance required: $100,000.00']
